{
  "stem": "10283.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Petain took all the Jews out of those camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the German Germans--- non-Jewish Germans he took back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Jewish Germans they took all to Drancy and-- for deportation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I even have the list, the-- what the-- Holocaust Museum in Washington sent me the list, the deportation list out of Drancy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my father's name is on it right at  the beginning, with his birth date and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he was not in the best condition already-- you know, two years in the French camps already.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he, he went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so did my uncle, apparently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But Werner was young.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was 18.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he had been liberated already by ORT, you know, the ORT organization was big in France.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was not quite 18.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he, he qualified as a child yet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was in an ORT school in France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And when the deportations started, the, the mayor of this little town came to the school and said, send-- tomorrow morning, the SS will come and get all the children.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Send the bigger boys and girls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Give them whatever you can.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And send them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They have to fend for themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they have a chance-- better the chance than sitting here and being picked up tomorrow morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he spoke very well, French.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very gifted for languages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the meantime, he spoke a very good French.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somehow, through months of walking during the night and sleeping in the fields during the day and working a little bit here and there in the hotels and on farms, he made his way to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he, he came into Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was already there.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
